#. type: delimited block . 4
#: documentation/content/en/books/handbook/advanced-networking/_index.adoc:2926
#, no-wrap
msgid "ifconfig_gif0_ipv6=\"inet6 MY_ASSIGNED_IPv6_TUNNEL_ENDPOINT_ADDR\"\n"
